{
  "stem": "95.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in the house, I mean, we were 24 hours with Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I-- and I liked-- I liked a lot of the holidays.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, Passover, to me, was just-- when you think of Passover, there's a great warmth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Even though we are very small-- I mean, when I was a small kid, that apartment was gigantic.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But when you go back to it now, even though I'm not that tall, but suddenly, they're little cubicles.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I mean, those rooms are like-- like toys, you know, like small-- for-- for dolls.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They are that small.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But during Passover, the whole family will go for the first seder.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there we are-- nephews and nieces and brothers and sisters and brothers in law.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we all sleep on the floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Everybody is there for two days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And it was just-- I must say, I didn't like the long seder, though, that went on forever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because my father just went through the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And there's one thing that I-- I was-- amazingly, I was the last one, the last child.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "When my mother-- my father had one brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The first one was a brother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Then he had two daughters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Then he had a son who died when he was six months old, and then he had four daughters and me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was the last one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they always picked on me, the girls, especially during Passover when you have to open the door, you know, for Elia-- what's his name?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eli-- you don't know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, I do know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For-- now it's gone right out of my brain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whoever-- whoever he is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- I used to call him [INAUDIBLE], which is not the right title.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] is something really-- but because I was scared, I opened the door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Right?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
